  "title": "Project Architect/ Project Designer",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Architectural industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Project Architect </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Project Architect</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Central</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, 9am to 6pm</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Basic + Bonus (GOOD BENEFITS!)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct site visits, research, and feasibility assessments to gather essential project data.</li>\n  <li>Develop conceptual and detailed architectural designs tailored to project requirements.</li>\n  <li>Prepare technical documentation, including CAD drawings, 3D renderings, and design presentations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with applicable design standards, building codes, and authority regulations.</li>\n  <li>Submit plans and documentation to relevant agencies and coordinate the approval process.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate closely with internal teams and external consultants to ensure design coordination and constructability.</li>\n  <li>Attend client and stakeholder meetings to present design proposals and manage feedback.</li>\n  <li>Monitor construction progress to verify alignment with design intent and resolve on-site issues as needed.</li>\n  <li>Support the delivery of sustainable, cost-effective, and high-quality architectural outcomes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least Degree in Architecture or a related field from a recognized institution.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of professional experience in architectural design and project delivery.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in design tools such as AutoCAD, Revit, SketchUp, and Adobe Creative Suite.</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of local regulatory frameworks, building codes, and submission processes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
